	bool "TIM8 DAC"
	default n
	depends on STM32L4_TIM8 && STM32L4_DAC
	---help---
		Reserve timer 8 for use by DAC

		Timer devices may be used for different purposes.  If STM32L4_TIM8 is
		defined then the following may also be defined to indicate that the
